Uthe kube sekuseshwa amaveni kwatholwa amabhokisi angu-40 anamaphakethe angu-500 kagwayi ngalinye. Ugwayi kuthiwa ungabiza uR900 000. Kuboshwe abasolwa abaneminyaka ephakathi kuka-28 no-54. Omunye umsolwa oneminyaka engu-33 ubuye wabekwa icala lokuba kwelakuleli ngokungemthetho. Abasolwa bazovela enkantolo maduze ngokutholwa nogwayi ongekho emthethweni. Ukhomishana wamaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal uthe ukuboshwa kwabasolwa kuzothumela umyalezo oshubile kwabashushumbisa ugwayi ongekho emthethweni.